WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:05.772 --> 00:00:09.276
He was betrayed by his own brother

00:00:10.124 --> 00:00:13.124
He lost his family

00:00:13.647 --> 00:00:17.647
He was trapped in a cavern

00:00:20.294 --> 00:00:23.294
Yet he became a man

00:00:25.217 --> 00:00:28.217
Life is made of many searches

00:00:28.979 --> 00:00:31.979
A search can last a lifetime

00:00:34.621 --> 00:00:37.621
but when a man discovers his greatest destiny,

00:00:38.605 --> 00:00:41.605
and understands that what is above

00:00:41.866 --> 00:00:44.866
is the same as below...

00:00:46.928 --> 00:00:49.928
He will discover

00:00:50.666 --> 00:00:53.666
The Wizard within himself

00:00:55.123 --> 00:00:58.123
Within each of us is a great purpose yet to be awoken

00:01:00.627 --> 00:01:03.627
This purpose will awaken in just the right moment

00:01:12.340 --> 00:01:15.340
The Great Spirit

00:01:17.210 --> 00:01:20.210
will guide him on his journey

00:01:21.111 --> 00:01:24.111
to find the Secret Garden

00:01:25.053 --> 00:01:28.053
and his search for the light

00:01:37.820 --> 00:01:39.820
He will cross deserts

00:01:42.002 --> 00:01:44.000
Face his fears

00:01:45.514 --> 00:01:47.510
He will fight against the Great Evil

00:01:49.064 --> 00:01:51.060
He will defy death

00:01:55.115 --> 00:01:58.120
If he wants to plant The Tree

00:01:59.987 --> 00:02:01.990
A book of Paola Lombardi

00:02:03.878 --> 00:02:07.880
The book of the Wizard

00:02:09.614 --> 00:02:11.610
Coming soon

